            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Place the<strong> smoked basa fillets</strong> on a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray</p><p>Drizzle them with a little <strong>olive oil</strong> and season with a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 12 min or until the basa is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/368.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
