            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Bring a pot with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Crack the <strong>egg<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> gently into the water and leave them for 3 min</p><p>Once done, gently transfer the<strong> </strong>eggs<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> with a slotted spoon to kitchen paper<strong> </strong>and season them with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – these are your <strong>poached eggs</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/368.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/368.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/368.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
