          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/368.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>potatoes</strong> to a low heat with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a splash of <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Mash until smooth, then add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>spinach</strong></p><p>Stir in the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>cheese</strong> and <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>spring onion</strong> and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>- this is your <strong>cheesy spinach mash</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/368.-step-7-x200.jpg",
